sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Workflow as 流程服务
  participant DB as MySQL
  participant Scope as 角色范围匹配
  actor Reviewer as 责任角色
  actor Applicant as 申请人

  Workflow->>DB: 读取 step.responsibleRoles
  Workflow->>DB: 查询拥有责任角色的用户
  loop 每个候选人
    Workflow->>Scope: roleMatchesApplicantScope(candidate, applicant)
    alt 范围覆盖且未被排除
      Scope-->>Workflow: 保留为收件人
    else 范围不覆盖
      Scope-->>Workflow: 丢弃
    end
  end
  Workflow->>DB: 写 notifications
  Reviewer-->>DB: H5/PC 拉取 /api/mobile/messages 或待办
  Applicant-->>DB: H5 拉取审核结果通知
